PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FAccording to the force, the victim, in
OL,8,Fher 20s, said she was followed and
OL,9,Fattacked after leaving Labyrinth Epsom
OL,10,Fnightclub.
OL,12,FThe attack is believed to have
OL,13,Foccurred between 2am and 4am on
OL,14,FSaturday outside Epsom Methodist
OL,15,FChurch in Ashley Road.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, footage posted on social
OL,18,Fmedia showed a large crowd of
OL,19,Fprotesters congregated in the town
OL,20,Fcentre.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FDozens of police officers could be
OL,8,Fseen wearing helmets and holding
OL,9,Fshields, with objects appearing to
OL,10,Fhave been thrown at them.
OL,12,FThe protest was promoted online by
OL,13,FDanny Tommo, a former associate of
OL,14,Fright-wing activist Tommy Robinson.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FDuring the demonstration a letter was
OL,8,Fread out in which a resident asked for
OL,9,Fmore information and reassurance from
OL,10,Fthe police after the assault,
OL,11,Fparticularly on whether any suspects
OL,12,Fhad been identified and detained and
OL,13,Fif there was still a risk to the
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,16,FThe group also blocked the road,
OL,17,Fcausing disruption to motorists,
OL,18,Fbefore leaving the scene at around
OL,19,F8pm, according to police.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FEast Surrey Chief Superintendent Mark
OL,8,FChapman said: "There was a significant
OL,9,Fpolice presence in Epsom town centre
OL,10,Fthis evening to support the group's
OL,11,Fright to lawful protest and minimise
OL,12,Fdisruption to the local community.
OL,14,F"I appreciate that this may have
OL,15,Fcaused concern to people in the town
OL,16,Fcentre, and I would like to reassure
OL,17,Fyou that our priority was to ensure
OL,18,Fthe safety of the wider public, as
OL,19,Fwell as the safety of those involved
OL,20,Fin the protest.
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,F"I also appreciate that there was some
OL,8,Fdisruption in the town centre while
OL,9,Fthe protest was taking place and I
OL,10,Fwould like to thank all those affected
OL,11,Ffor their patience.
OL,13,F"We respect the right to lawful
OL,14,Fprotest and will facilitate this
OL,15,Fwherever possible where it is safe to
OL,16,Fdo so. However, criminal offences and
OL,17,Fpublic disorder will not be tolerated,
OL,18,Fand we will always take robust action
OL,19,Fagainst anyone who commits a criminal
OL,20,Foffence."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
