OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FOfficers remained in the town centre
OL,8,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,10,FThe force urged people not to
OL,11,Fspeculate about the descriptions of
OL,12,Fthe suspects in an earlier update,
OL,13,Fsaying it did not have enough
OL,14,Finformation to provide descriptions.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
