CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FMerseyside Police were criticised for
OL,8,Fnot revealing the ethnicity of Axel
OL,9,FRudakubana when he was arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of murder after he killed
OL,11,Fthree young girls at a Taylor Swift-
OL,12,Fthemed dance class in Southport in
OL,13,FJuly 2024.
OL,15,FWithin hours of the attack, posts on
OL,16,Fthe internet claimed the suspect was a
OL,17,F17-year-old asylum seeker who had come
OL,18,Fto the country by boat.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
