PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776427866
OL,3,CPolice say disorder will not be
OL,4,Ctolerated after protests over 'rape'
OL,5,Cin Epsom
OL,7,FIn August last year, police forces
OL,8,Fwere told to share suspects' ethnicity
OL,9,Fand nationality with the public after
OL,10,Fauthorities were accused of covering
OL,11,Fup offences by asylum seekers.
OL,13,FGarrington Property Finders named
OL,14,FEpsom the 12th most desirable place to
OL,15,Flive in England and Wales in its 2026
OL,16,Flist.
OL,18,FIt said the average cost of a home in
OL,19,Fthe area is #712,105.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
